{"tid":1692882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不論政見，尋日太古單嘢爆左個大問題","createTime":"2019-11-04T09:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T10:41:26.000Z","uid":50457,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c4660580b4d600a09aed4442843a87ef75b3c709","tid":1692882,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:46:27.000Z","msg":"即使平日精神狀態的人，呢五個月情緒應該有一定的抑壓，或者大喜大落<br />\n<br />\n而香港政府一直都唔處理社區的精神病人，而之前有港台節目都有講，呢幾個月好多人都情緒不穩<br />\n<br />\n結果只會好似尋日的情況不斷爆發，潛在社會的精神病人大爆發。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家日後出街，真係要超級小心，唔好淨係掛住篤機</span>"},{"pid":"54046512e93fd9b456535636e7685e661a1efcb9","tid":1692882,"uid":27243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:57:20.000Z","msg":"好多小丑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c0c24063cf834ca94709f1ffe605897ec6186d","tid":1692882,"uid":283725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:58:50.000Z","msg":"我住果層都有個痴線佬。成日啤住人<br />\n<br />\n好想屌佢。又驚佢發作"},{"pid":"e934386f6aa7857ed874956dcd39c657481a01c3","tid":1692882,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66c0c24063cf834ca94709f1ffe605897ec6186d","tid":1692882,"uid":283725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:58:50.000Z","msg":"我住果層都有個痴線佬。成日啤住人<br />\n<br />\n好想屌佢。又驚佢發作"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:03:32.000Z","msg":"小心啲好，周街都有隨時有失控精神病人"},{"pid":"b4456817694940627acbc37e821740b46ec76150","tid":1692882,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66c0c24063cf834ca94709f1ffe605897ec6186d","tid":1692882,"uid":283725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:58:50.000Z","msg":"我住果層都有個痴線佬。成日啤住人<br />\n<br />\n好想屌佢。又驚佢發作"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:05:11.000Z","msg":"屌痴線佬真係自己蝕底，鶳都要等有人幫手自保"},{"pid":"d71ce3dfcea22c5f1fac65e732454cf51945a728","tid":1692882,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4456817694940627acbc37e821740b46ec761